Jailor- (7)
- Can pick a person every day end to imprison, for 2 phases.
- Any jailed person is protected from all attacks and is role blocked for that duration. The person is informed they were jailed.
- The jailor cannot jail the same person twice in a row, unless the jailor has died and respawned.
- Action is day end. Has no cooldown. Cannot jail themselves. Jailing is weak protection. Jailing is not a visiting action.
- Respawns in 6 phases.
